paragraphs.title: Convert XML to CSV files and Load annual data into HDFS
paragraphs.text:
%sh 

# Please run the script load.sh on your computer before running this.

# Convert all the XML files into CSV files
python /extract_xml.py /PrixCarburants_annuel_2007.xml > prix2007.csv
python /extract_xml.py /PrixCarburants_annuel_2008.xml > prix2008.csv
python /extract_xml.py /PrixCarburants_annuel_2009.xml > prix2009.csv
python /extract_xml.py /PrixCarburants_annuel_2010.xml > prix2010.csv
python /extract_xml.py /PrixCarburants_annuel_2011.xml > prix2011.csv
python /extract_xml.py /PrixCarburants_annuel_2012.xml > prix2012.csv
python /extract_xml.py /PrixCarburants_annuel_2013.xml > prix2013.csv
python /extract_xml.py /PrixCarburants_annuel_2014.xml > prix2014.csv
python /extract_xml.py /PrixCarburants_annuel_2015.xml > prix2015.csv
python /extract_xml.py /PrixCarburants_annuel_2016.xml > prix2016.csv
python /extract_xml.py /PrixCarburants_annuel_2017.xml > prix2017.csv

# Put data into HDFS
hadoop fs -put prix* /user/maria_dev/data/

# Change permission to load the data into table
hadoop fs -chmod 777 /user/maria_dev/data/*

# Remove data 
rm prix*

%jdbc(hive)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS gas_temp (id_pdv STRING, cp STRING, pop CHAR(1), latitude INT, longitude INT, day STRING, id_carburant STRING, nom_carburant STRING, prix INT)
	ROW FORMAT DELIMITED
		FIELDS TERMINATED BY '59'
		LINES TERMINATED BY '\n'
paragraphs.title: Create a temporary Hive table

paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive)

LOAD DATA INPATH '/user/maria_dev/data/' OVERWRITE INTO TABLE gas_temp
paragraphs.title: Load annual data into the temporary Hive table

paragraphs.text:
%sh

# Please run the script daily.sh before running this.

# Convert the XML file into CSV file
python /extract_xml.py /daily.xml > daily.csv

# Put data into HDFS
hadoop fs -put daily.csv /user/maria_dev/data/

# Change permission to load the data into table
hadoop fs -chmod 777 /user/maria_dev/data/daily.csv

# Remove data
rm daily.csv
paragraphs.title: Convert XML files to CSV files and Load daily data into HDFS

paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive)

LOAD DATA INPATH '/user/maria_dev/data/daily.csv' INTO TABLE gas_temp
paragraphs.title: Load daily data into the temporary Hive table

paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive)

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS gas
paragraphs.title: Remove the gas table if it already exists

paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive)

CREATE TABLE gas
	STORED AS PARQUETFILE
	AS SELECT *, substr(day, 1, 10) AS Jour, substr(day, 6, 5) AS daymonth, substr(day, 1, 4) AS Year, substr(cp, 1, 2) AS dep
		FROM gas_temp
paragraphs.title: Create a Hive table stored in Parquet file format

paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive)

ALTER TABLE gas CHANGE Jour Jour DATE
paragraphs.title: Change the type of one column
Plot the evolution of gas price for a given sale point and a given year to compare the different gas

paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive)

SELECT id_pdv, nom_carburant, prix, Jour, daymonth, year FROM gas 
    WHERE Jour NOT LIKE '' AND id_pdv = '${PDV}' AND nom_carburant = '${Gas Name}'
	ORDER BY Jour
paragraphs.title: Plot the evolution of a gas price since the data are collected for a given sale point

paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive)

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS temp
paragraphs.title: Drop the table temp if it exists

paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive)

CREATE TABLE temp
	STORED AS PARQUETFILE
	AS SELECT DISTINCT id_pdv, nom_carburant, year FROM gas
	        WHERE nom_carburant NOT LIKE ''
paragraphs.title: Plot the evolution of the number of sale points which sales some gas

paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive)

SELECT year, count(*) AS count FROM temp
    WHERE nom_carburant LIKE 'E10'
	GROUP BY year

    WHERE dep = ${Department}
	GROUP BY year
